{"tid":801038,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會展新翼裂紋貫穿樓底","createTime":"2018-08-31T10:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T11:47:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"edb8e36a3b040955e5bbc3520e23058ab9b80e19","tid":801038,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:09:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180831/20488709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F20488709&d=ZLoo38Xlgln5pGjbkuEY%2BLDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=5d7974fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F20488709&h=e18da54d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180831/20488709</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月31日 <br />\n<br />\n會展新翼裂紋貫穿樓底<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180831/large/31la3p20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F31la3p20.jpg&h=e2b75149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【會展新翼】會展新翼多處出現裂紋。何柏佳攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】沙中綫會展站工程在會議道及博覽道一帶錄得沉降超標，會展中心新翼多處牆身都出現裂紋，地面亦凹凸不平，懷疑與沉降有關。有工程師認為，有關裂紋未必影響會展的樓宇結構，不過有可能導致外牆剝落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家估計沉降引起<br />\n<br />\n根據傳真社報道，會展中心新翼底部多處牆身滿佈裂紋，部份牆身有曾經修補過的痕迹，不過未能遮蓋裂紋。當中以博覽道向北的一面牆最為嚴重，整幅牆滿佈髮絲般的裂紋，每隔三、四步便有一條較明顯的裂紋，部份由地下蔓延至樓底。會展博覽道中靠東面一座構築物的牆身，更出現大範圍龜裂。會議道停車場出入口的地面亦有凹凸不平的情況。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述結構工程師倪學仁表示，相信有關裂紋較大可能由沉降引起，部份外牆出現打斜的裂紋，可能是由於會展的主體結構座落在樁上，而部份非主結構牆等構築物未必座落在樁上，由於兩者在不同地基之上，當出現土地下陷時便會產生扯力，導致非主結構的外牆出現裂紋。<br />\n<br />\n倪學仁表示，以肉眼所見，外牆的裂紋未必會產生大範圍或大面積的危險，不過若然外圍有裝飾物，例如紙皮石，便有可能因此脫落跌下擊傷途人。<br />\n<br />\n■記者麥志榮  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n131處超標20處持續惡化　全綫淪陷舊區14幢樓沉降<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n被揭大幅放寬停工標準<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵拒按政府要求加固<br />\n<br />\n選擇性放料避傳媒質詢<br />\n<br />\n西九內地口岸年租僅千元<br />\n<br />\n131處超標　20處持續惡化全綫淪陷　舊區14幢樓沉降<br />\n<br />\n被揭大幅放寬停工標準<br />\n<br />\n施工後改設計致沉降　路政署批准土瓜灣站　少裝一層工字鐵"},{"pid":"e6df49eedb4e762afdcf1e7c2b680b48973faf2a","tid":801038,"uid":39550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:10:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ba1f7fe51068b306017bf9042b2b224819a6b6","tid":801038,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:11:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我話ok就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span>"},{"pid":"092cd7a479ecc0d13fe5f939a46d6ce79aac7141","tid":801038,"uid":49697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:11:51.000Z","msg":"我話ok就ok嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd53569d9cd5ccbb1f79c86c386c0f1cc411598d","tid":801038,"uid":22624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:12:15.000Z","msg":"香港個金漆招牌咁就冇咗"},{"pid":"9202458227153e9c3ea53f9957310be1bd7ee914","tid":801038,"uid":61748,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:12:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b50972a9ec8cd22b0db497dba6d323de3400dc5","tid":801038,"uid":66527,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"tvb完全無報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5444c17dc89cc7b7e1efa56c3eae4e225f248d30","tid":801038,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no